{"tid":1393181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]吳三毛全面進場, 想引清兵入關","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:52:45.000Z","uid":54785,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b4f97dae77df73d9f1482f353932e58107cc61","tid":1393181,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"連登出現大量風向post, 以黑暗兵法為名目, 清算黑警為理由, 想帶風向令香港人打開鐵閘放解放軍入城, 此舉有如引狼入室, 好似玩玩筆仙碟仙咁, 易請難送。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人出聲叫解放軍入城, 國際社會只好認同呢個係香港人意願, 無法提供協助, 因為中共名正言順, 我地就失去向國際社會求助嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n到時老解治港, 後果難以想像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要小心呢堆吳三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd5634052b539f067b30f77a4a24d59e8cec475","tid":1393181,"uid":264868,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"其實一出老解 最傷係中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ac770346a3c12327d8906bae00df6e1b34e107","tid":1393181,"uid":91721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0bd5634052b539f067b30f77a4a24d59e8cec475","tid":1393181,"uid":264868,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"其實一出老解 最傷係中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"前提係香港人無要求解放軍支援嘅意願"},{"pid":"8f4b3200680bd7bcbc46af5708591ea74ca921b4","tid":1393181,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"9e5f87233b9cc095e2858edc840b7cf4fa1ce052","tid":1393181,"uid":273272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:16: